Section 4: Debugging Scenario 2
Command:
docker run -p 8080:80 nginx

Cannot access in browser.

Questions
Possible causes?
How to verify container is running?
Which command helps inspect networking?

Solutions:-

1. Possible Causes
Container not running
Port already in use
Firewall blocking
Wrong binding
Docker network issue

2. Verify Container
docker ps
docker ps -a

3. Networking Debug
docker port <id>
docker inspect <id>
curl localhost:8080
